GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 31st July, 2012
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 31st July, 2012:
(i)
The Prime Minister relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Finance.
(ii)
Shri P. Chidambaram relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Home
Affairs and assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Finance;
(iii)
Shri Sushilkumar Shinde relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Power
and assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Home Affairs; and
Shri M. Veerappa Moily assumed the additional charge of the office of the Minister of
Power. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Corporate
Affairs.
(iv)
